>Construction of pTarg2
acquire oligo targAf
acquire oligo targAr
acquire oligo targBf
acquire oligo targBr
acquire plasmid p20N5
acquire plasmid pTargetF
PCR targAf,targAr on p20N5	(1200 bp, pcrA)
PCR targBf,targBr on pTargetF	(1172 bp, pcrB)
Assemble pcrA,pcrB	(Gibson, pTarg2)
Transform pTarg2	(Mach1, Amp)
